programme.title: World Watch: Rise of The Machine Ep17
programme.desc: Dokumentari yang mendedahkan ciptaan paling mengejutkan yang menjadikan mesin terbesar dan paling ikonik. Episod kali ini membawa penonton melihat teknologi kereta lori pengangkut super yang berupaya memindahkan Atacama Large Milimeter Array, sebuah system yang terdiri daripada 66 teleskop radio yang mengukur radiasi electromagnet pada kadar wavelength milimeter dan submilimeter. Jentera pengangkut dengan 28 tayar yang boleh berpusing 360 darjah ini mampu mengangkut beban dengan berat sehingga 115 tan.

programme.title: Setia Menunggumu Ep9

programme.title: Suluhkan Aku Cahaya
programme.desc: Syarif maklumkan sebenarnya dia jahil agama dan sebelum ini hanya lakonan sahaja. Zulaikha pada mulanya kecewa dengan sikap suaminya namun dia demi cinta dia ingin membantu Syarif. Perbualan mereka didengari oleh Ustaz Jamal lalu Ustaz Jamal lantas dia meminta mereka untuk tinggal dengannya.

programme.title: Secebis Rindu Ep1
programme.desc: Rasya Aleeya dan Syed Reeza mula berkenalan melalui SMS, membina hubungan cinta walaupun Rasya mengalami paranoia dan Reeza dikenali sebagai lelaki yang suka menggoda. Hubungan mereka diuji apabila Rasya sukar mempercayai Reeza, dipengaruhi masa lalunya dan hasutan Adri, rakan Reeza. Akhirnya, Rasya berkahwin dengan Fahmi, sepupu dan pilihan keluarganya, tetapi perkahwinan itu gagal. Reeza yang terluka terpaksa bertunang dengan Hilda, pilihan keluarganya. Namun, perasaan mereka berdua kembali bercambah selepas bertemu semula di Dubai. Rasya berasa bersalah atas kesilapan lalu tetapi akhirnya mereka berjaya mengatasi salah faham dan ketakutan yang menghalang cinta mereka. Rancangan Reeza untuk menguji perasaan Rasya berjaya memecahkan ego dan ketakutannya. Mereka akhirnya berkahwin dan mendapat restu keluarga, membuktikan cinta sejati mereka mampu bertahan walaupun diuji pelbagai cabaran.

programme.title: Abang Lori Ohsem S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Hubungan Luqman dan Lufia, dalam tak sedar semakin rapat apabila dia sering dihantui Lufia untuk menagih ganti rugi atas kecelakaan yang berlaku di Airport. Luqman pula dibuang kerja dari menjadi seorang cleaner akibat dari insiden semalam. Cigo cuba mengajak Luqman bekerja sebagai pemandu lori di syarikat Cigo bekerja. Apabila mengetahui yang gaji membawa lori begitu lumayan, Luqman bersetuju dan bermulalah kehidupan Luqman sebagai pemandu lori. Pertemuan kali kedua Luqman dan Lufia di atas jalan raya, apabila dia hampir melanggar kereta Lufia dan tanpa rasa simpati, Lufia menaikkan ganti ruginya terhadapa Luqman. Di kampung pula, Mira mula mengetahui yang Nek Wan selama ini berahsia dengannya tentang hutang lapuk arwah datuk Luqman. Mira cuba untuk berkongsi masalah tersebut dengan Luqman.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep1
programme.desc: Meskipun Farah sedang menunggu saat diijabkabulkan, namun dia masih dalam dilemma untuk menjadi isteri Lukman. Dia masih keliru dengan keputusannya; antara Amanah arwah Sarah dengan keikhlasannya menerima abang iparnya sebagai suami. Baik Lukman mahupun Farah, kedua-duanya terpaksa maniskan wajah di majlis pernikahan mereka demi menjaga hati Zahin dan kedua-dua orang tua. Di sebalik kegembiraan, ada hati yang tercarik luka dengan pernikahan mereka. Lantaran terlalu kecewa, Myra sanggup bertindak di luar kawalan hingga menyebabkannya kemalangan dan koma. Joshua muncul untuk membantu Myra lalu membawanya ke hospital. Lukman pula resah kerana tidak dapat menjejak Myra setelah Myra hilang begitu sahaja ketika majlis pernikahannya berlangsung. Farah kecewa apabila Lukman berterus terang yang dia takkan menyentuh Farah kerana dia hanya setia dan cintakan arwah isterinya, Sarah.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep2
programme.desc: Farah masih terkilan dengan kata-kata Lukman pada malam pertama pernikahan mereka apatah lagi Lukman menyebut nama Myra dalam tidurnya. Farah berasa kurang senang apabila Lukman berpura-pura romantis dengannya di depan famili. Budi terkejut apabila Lukman datang ke pejabat sehari selepas bernikah seakan-akan mahu mengelak daripada Farah. Lukman terkejut setelah menerima surat perletakan jawatan Myra yang ditinggalkan di atas meja. Papa menegur Lukman yang berperangai seperti orang bujang dan balik lewat meskipun sudah berkahwin. Akibat terasa dengan teguran Papa, Lukman bertindak mengajak Farah balik ke rumahnya. Farah cuba menyesuaikan diri dengan keadaan rumah Lukman yang bersepah dan seakan tidak terurus selepas kematian Sarah. Lukman cemburu dan mula syak wasangka apabila melihat Farah bersama Nazim di kafe.

programme.title: The Gadis Ep1
programme.desc: Mengisahkan dua gadis remaja Alina dan adiknya Alisa. Mereka tinggal dengan bapanya yang mengalami lumpuh, ibu mereka telah meninggal dunia. Alina terpaksa berhenti sekolah walaupun mendapat kelulusan cemerlang dalam peperiksaan SPM. Beliau terpaksa bekerja mencuci dan membersih rumah penduduk, termasuk rumah Nek Timah dan Imah bagi menampung keperluan keluarga. Alina tidak mahu Alisa berhenti sekolah sepertinya. Alisa pelajar cemerlang, sedang bersaing dengan Mei Fen menjadi pelajar cemerlang bagi mendapat hadiah RM20 ribu. Satu hari, Lina pergi menjenguk Nek TImah dan bertembung dengan kekasih lamanya, Shazman anak kepada Imah yang kini berjaya menghabiskan pelajaran di kolej. Lina ditegur Nad, kawan lama sekolah Lina dan juga cucu kepada Nek Timah ketika berada di rumah Nek Timah. Lina terpaku dengan kecantikan dan kekayaan Nad. Lina ternampak mesej dari Mika di telefon Nad dan mula ragu-ragu dengan pekerjaannya. programme.title: Plan B Ep13
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Iris disoalsiat polis. Dia mendakwa dirinya tidak langsung mengetahui tujuan Khai sebenarnya sehingga dia terlibat dalam rompakan. Namun Khai, Mika, Que dan Iris disabit kesalahan kerana merompak secara berkumpulan dengan bersenjata api dan dihukum penjara sepanjang hayat. Setelah beberapa kali percubaan dalam rayuan kes tersebut, Iris hanya dipenjara beberapa tahun sahaja. Bagaimanapun Khai akan berusaha memboloskan diri dari penjara dan dia berjanji untuk membunuh Iris.

programme.title: The Secret Of Sinchanee
programme.desc: Seorang pemandu trak tunda industri yang mengalami insomnia kembali ke rumah zaman kanak-kanaknya selepas kematian bapanya, untuk mengetahui bahawa kehadiran paranormal telah tinggal di rumah itu dan menghantui tanah suci yang dibina di atasnya.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep5
programme.desc: Pertemuan Din dan Anat mengenai cek yang tertangguh bertukar menjadi pertengkaran, tapi rahsia yang dapat memecahbelahkan keluarga Tan Sri Alif muncul.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep6
programme.desc: Noramina kagum dengan kemahiran bertarung Uzair dan menawar pekerjaan sebagai pengawal peribadinya. Uzair kini mempunyai pekerjaan yang sesuai dan boleh menyewa tempat tinggal sendiri. Hatta mula sedar ada sesuatu yang baik dan istimewa pada Uzair. Uzair mula mesra dengan Noramina.

programme.title: Model Family Ep1
programme.desc: Sebuah keluarga ibu bapa tunggal (Yu Xiang dan Tong Tong) berpindah ke kawasan kejiranan baharu di mana kehidupan semua orang nampak sempurna. Walau bagaimanapun, keadaan mungkin kelihatan cerah di luar, rahsia gelap dan seram menyerbu setiap keluarga dari dalam, dan tidak ada yang benar-benar seperti yang kelihatan.

programme.title: Bodyguard
programme.desc: Seorang lelaki yang kehilangan cinta dan keinginannya untuk hidup bekerja bersama rakan-rakan zaman kanak-kanaknya di sebuah syarikat pinjaman persendirian. Suatu hari, dia bertemu dengan seorang wanita yang sedang dikejar oleh penyerang yang tidak dikenali. Wanita itu merupakan satu-satunya pewaris kepada sebuah korporat. Dia sedang diburu oleh seseorang yang cuba merampas syarikat tersebut. Sementara itu, pemilik syarikat pinjaman tersebut mula mencari wanita itu.

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil 1
programme.desc: Abang Long Fadil, seorang lelaki yang sentiasa berangan bahawa kehidupannya seperti seorang gangster. Namun, apabila sahabat baiknya, Malik, dimasukkan ke penjara, keadaan menjadi lebih huru-hara, dan angan-angannya mungkin tidak jauh daripada realiti.

programme.title: Jwanita
programme.desc: Jwanita (Maya Karin) yang sakit mental dan didera oleh Ibu / Dukun (Umie Aida) dan bapa angkatnya (Radin Intan), yang mengamalkan ilmu hitam. Jwanita kemudian bertemu dengan Farhan (Bront Palarae) yang menjaganya selepas dia membunuh kedua ibu bapa angkatnya dalam satu peristiwa tragis.

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil 2
programme.desc: Kisah mengenai Fadil yang terjerumus ke dalam dunia mafia yang diketuai oleh Taji Samprit dan anaknya, Wak Doyok. Satu insiden menyebabkan Inspektor Wahab dan Inspektor Shuib mengesyaki Fadil sebagai Tiger, seorang pembunuh upahan profesional.

programme.title: Two Sisters
programme.desc: Selepas seorang gadis dibebaskan dari rumah sakit jiwa, dia disatukan semula dengan kakaknya dan mereka kembali ke rumah keluarga yang ditinggalkan. Namun, kedua-dua beradik itu menyimpan rahsia gelap dan tragis keluarga yang mula terungkap selepas kepulangan mereka.

programme.title: The Secret Suster Ngesot Urban
programme.desc: Mengetahui bahawa bapanya telah berkahwin dengan seorang wanita sebayanya, Kanaya meninggalkan rumah, hanya untuk mengalami kemalangan yang menyebabkan dia di hospital berhantu.

programme.title: Pelepas Saka
programme.desc: Sejak pulang ke kampung, Alisya sering diganggu dengan bayangan seorang wanita tua dan kadang-kala dia akan mendengar bunyi buaian yang berayun di luar rumah. Alisya juga sering diganggu dengan mimpi yang bukan-bukan menyebabkan dia terfikir-fikir apa yang sedang terjadi padanya. Suatu malam, usai saja majlis doa selamat di rumah Adnan, Asiah telah melakukan upacara melepaskan sakanya pada Haider. Setelah melepaskan sakanya, wajah Asiah berubah menjadi sangat tua dan badannya membongkok. Asiah hilang jejak selepas itu. Haider tidak menyedari bahawa dirinya kini didampingi oleh saka Asiah dan perangainya mula berubah. Dia menjadi panas-baran, suka makan telur mentah, sentiasa panas dan mula mengsyaki hubungan antara Raden dan Alisya. Raden juga diganggu oleh saka Asiah dengan menjelmakan diri sebagai Alisya. Raden mula tidak sedap hati dan memberitahu hal ini pada Adnan. Raden juga berusaha mencari punca setiap gangguan yang berlaku di rumah tersebut sehingga membawanya ke rumah Asiah. Di situ barulah Raden tahu tentang kisah yang terjadi.

programme.title: Larian Terakhir
programme.desc: Haziq, seorang anak tunggal kepada Mariam yang mempunyai bakat dalam larian pantas, sering berhadapan dengan dugaan kehidupan sehinggakan dia terpaksa meninggalkan ibunya yang sakit. Tanpa disedarinya, pertemuannya dengan Jalal telah memerangkapnya dalam sebuah sindiket jenayah. Walaupun Haziq dijanjikan peluang untuk memperbaiki hidupnya, Amelia sentiasa mengawasi setiap pergerakannya dengan teliti. Larian Terakhir adalah sebuah filem yang menggabungkan genre aksi dan sukan dengan penampilan pelakon-pelakon seperti Fattah Amin, Amyra Rosli, dan Fahrin Ahmad, di mana setiap larian akan sampai ke kemuncaknya.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong
programme.desc: Seorang pejuang muda bernama Kham mesti pergi ke Australia untuk mendapatkan semula gajah yang dicurinya. Dengan bantuan detektif Australia kelahiran Thailand, Kham mesti menghadapi semua yang datang, termasuk kumpulan yang diketuai oleh seorang wanita jahat dan dua pengawal peribadinya yang maut.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Di Seri Setia, Black dan Sofia bekerjasama untuk menghalang satu pembunuhan yang berpotensi untuk berlaku. Semasa berada di sana, Black terimbas kembali masa lalu Malik, satu fenomena yang membingungkannya. Pemergian mereka ini juga merupakan titik perubahan cara Sofia melihat keupayaannya. Kesanggupan Sofia menggadaikan nyawanya untuk menyelamatkan nyawa orang lain memperbaharui tanggapan Black terhadapnya. Adakah cinta mula berputik? Black tertarik dan pada masa yang sama bingung dengan perasaannya terhadap Sofia, satu perasaan yang asing buat Black, seorang yang mementingkan diri. Tetapi hari yang bersinar menjadi pudar apabila Black kembali ke rumah dan mendapati bilik tersembunyi Malik telah digeledah dan dikosongkan. Sementara itu, pembunuh upahan telah meragut nyawa seorang lagi mangsa dan Detektif Borhan mendapati kematian itu ada kaitan dengan pembunuhan Nurul Najwa.

Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: The Hollow One
programme.desc: Rachel dan Anna pulang ke rumah dua tahun selepas kematian ibu mereka, dan dapati bandar itu ditinggalkan dengan rumah mereka dalam keadaan kacau dan kotor. Apabila Rachel mula mengalami halusinasi mengenai ibu mereka yang sudah meninggal dan sesuatu artifak purba, petunjuk-petunjuk menakutkan mula terbongkar mengenai masa lalu keluarga mereka.

programme.title: On Halloween
programme.desc: Satu siri kematian dan kehilangan kejam membawa kembali kepada legenda bandar tentang badut pembunuh bersiri. Sekumpulan pelajar kolej akan menghadapi mimpi ngeri terburuk mereka, apabila Badut jahat ini kembali dari masa lalu pada Halloween.

programme.title: Minyak Dagu
programme.desc: Minyak Dagu mengisahkan tentang Azman yang berdendam dengan bekas tunangnya Emelda dan disebabkan terlalu dendam dan mengikut pujukan daripada kawannya, Azman telah berjumpa bomoh, Wak Minarjo seorang pawang hebat minyak dagu. Emelda yang memutuskan pertunangan dengan Azman demi mengikut cakap kedua-dua orang tuanya bahawa Johan adalah seorang calon suami yang baik dan boleh menjamin masa depan Emelda, nak dibandingkan Azman yang hanya seorang jurujual yang sering tak ada untungnya.

programme.title: Plan B Ep12
programme.desc: Mengisahkan pasukan polis mengepung premis awam di mana Khai dan Iris bersembunyi dan menculik beberapa perkerja sebagai tebusan. Sebelum ini Mika yang cedera di dada akibat ditembak polis turut berada dalam premis itu. Que dibawa oleh Inspektor Faris untuk berunding dengan Khai supaya membebaskan tebusan. Khai hanya membebaskan dua tebusan setelah syarat menyerahkan Que kepadanya dipenuhi. Kedua-dua ibu bapa Khai dan Mika turut berada di tempat kejadian itu. Setelah mengubah aliran CCTV, beberapa anggota polis berjaya merempuh masuk ke premis itu. Khai, Iris, Que dan Mika diberkas polis.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep5
programme.desc: Pertemuan Din dan Anat mengenai cek yang tertangguh bertukar menjadi pertengkaran, tapi rahsia yang dapat memecahbelahkan keluarga Tan Sri Alif muncul.

programme.desc: Ashikin dan Uzair kembali bersama tetapi Imran sedaya upaya mendapatkan Ashikin kembali. Rakan-rakan Uzair datang menyokong Uzair dan Ashikin. Uzair terkejut apabila Hatta datang berlawan dengannya menentang Imran. Mereka cuba melarikan diri dari bandar tetapi Imran menggunakan Ajeeb mempunyai umpan.

programme.title: Jailangkung Sandekala
programme.desc: Keganasan ghaib berpusat pada sebuah keluarga kecil yang terdiri daripada Adrian dan isterinya Sandra, bersama dua anak mereka, Niki dan Kinan, yang sedang bercuti ke luar bandar.

programme.title: Kasih Farra
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Farra yang bercinta dengan Lokman, seorang lelaki yang jauh lebih tua daripada usianya. Lokman baru pulang ke Malaysia selepas lebih 20 tahun merantau ke luar negara. Tanpa pengetahuan Lokman, Farra ialah anak kepada bekas kekasihnya, Zura. Dalam masa yang sama, Zura sedang mencari Lokman untuk meminta maaf atas apa yang berlaku kepada hubungan mereka di masa lampau.

programme.title: Ali Setan
programme.desc: Ali pelajar universiti yang nakal dan suka bergurau berjumpa Asmidar ketika dalam perjalanan ke universiti. Ali selalu mencari jalan untuk mengusik Asmidar, lama kelamaan perasaan cinta mula berputik antara mereka berdua. Konflik mula terjadi apabila Ali sebenarnya sudah berkahwin dengan Tipah namun atas sebab terpaksa.

programme.title: Nylea & Harris
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Harris yang terpaksa bekerja sebagai pelayan walaupun dia memiliki kelulusan tinggi. Dia kemudiannya berjaya mendapat kerja sebagai arkitek di sebuah firma milik Tan Sri Kadir. Tugas pertama Harris ialah untuk menyiapkan sebuah rumah untuk anak perempuan Tan Sri Kadir iaitu Nylea. Pada mulanya Harris dan Nylea sering bertengkar namun lama kelamaan timbul bibit-bibit percintaan antara mereka berdua. Walau bagaimanapun, muncul pula Chris, bekas tunangan Nylea ke dalam hidup mereka yang membuatkan Harris sangat kecewa.

programme.title: Way to Health (M) Ep337
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Way to Health (M) Ep338
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Top Singers (T) Ep653
programme.desc: The show 'Top Singers' aims to spotlight outstanding Taiwanese singers and composers, setting a new standard in the industry. Combining elements of competition, variety, and personal stories, the show welcomes participants of all ages. Its goals include discovering grassroots talent, innovating Taiwanese song performance styles, and involving more local talent in song composition to infuse new life into Taiwanese music.

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep1010
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: Dear Mom (M) Ep42
programme.desc: Feng-Yi Li handles everything in the house while her husband, Shu-An, lounges and daydreams. She constantly worries about the love lives of their four daughters. Yi-Wan starts a relationship with a gang leaders son despite claiming to have never dated. Qing-Qing may be having an affair with a married man. Xiao-Xi is infatuated with the school team captain but is unaware of "the others." An-Qing returns from the US with her son after a failed marriage. When Feng-Yi suddenly disappears, the sisters realize they've neglected their mother, who has always supported them. Now they must find her and get their lives back on track.

programme.title: Kung Fu Mahjong 2
programme.desc: Fanny appears to be an ordinary housewife but is in fact a mahjong expert. Deeply in love with her husband, she loses to a seductive woman, Curvy, both on the mahjong table and in competing for her husbands love. With the help from her mahjong master, Fanny vows to take on Curvy in the Mahjong King tournament!

programme.title: I Believe
programme.desc: Chu Chu has been waiting for her first love for 10 years but he marries someone else in the end. As she loses faith in love, she meets a wedding planner and a handsome and rich man, who both help her get over her ex-boyfriend. As Chu Chu feels the same love from them, she must make up her mind. Who will she choose in the end?

programme.title: Chungking Express
programme.desc: Two Hong Kong urban love stories depicting two Hong Kong policemen, both jilted by ex-lovers and falling in love again. One falls for a mysterious female underworld figure while the other is in love with a beautiful and witty server at a fast food restaurant he frequents.

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real Chosen Sleuth instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: Detective Dee and Nine-storey Demon Building
programme.desc: A series of strange incidents happen at the Tangs demon building but Detective Dee finds no clue. Dee finds the master of the family suspicious when he speaks with him, and when the eldest daughter Miss Tang secretly informs Dee about Mr Tangs strange behavior and the fact that she is kept under surveillance, Dee vows to unveil the truth.

programme.title: American Dreams in China
programme.desc: During the economic reform period in the 80s, three undergraduates are brought together by a common ambition to live the American dream.

programme.title: Divergence
programme.desc: Three men are going beyond what their jobs require them to do. An ill-fated police detective runs into a woman during his investigation on a money laundering case, a lawyer protects a corrupt businessman from law and a ruthless killer violates his code to get involved in a police investigation. These three men are thrown together by circumstance...

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident

programme.title: Detrimental
programme.desc: You Ji Ren is a blind man who works at a factory in an outlying island. When the factory is cut off from the outside world by a hurricane one day, a monster appears and turns whoever sees it into black shadows. As You cannot see the monster, he is able to help other coworkers leave safely and fight to kill the monster!

programme.title: Naked Soldier
programme.desc: When Interpol agent Long busted a billion-dollar drug deal 15 years ago, the cartel took revenge and killed his family. The cartel boss, Madame Rose, even kidnaps and raises Longs daughter, Phoenix, to become a skilled assassin. Only when Phoenix is about to kill Long did she discover the startling fact about her true identity

programme.title: One and Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the clubs top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: Silent Code
programme.desc: Reporter Lan is tasked to research news from the internet, and stumbles across a popular BBS forum, Dream Board. Xiang, the forum founder, creates space for netizens to share dreams and ideas, but ended up being the subject of a heated debate due to a leaked video. As Lan digs for the truth, she finds things are more complicated than it seems...

programme.title: Ip Man 3
programme.desc: When some gangsters led by a ruthless American property developer force a school to sell their land, Ip Man fights to protect it. Subsequently, Ip Man is challenged by another Wing Chun master Zhang Tian Zhi for the Grandmaster title. Ip Man accepts the challenge for the sake of his family and disciples, and wins the duel for the title.

programme.title: The Eagle Shooting Heroes
programme.desc: Executive produced by Wong Kar Wai, The Eagle Shooting Heroes is loosely based on Louis Chas classics. Whilst mistaken identity and rampant gender confusion are on the menu, Sammo Hungs action direction and the incredible all-star casts also keep the laughs and thrills coming in this Hong Kong-style crazy comedy.

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Marriage With A Liar
programme.desc: Kiki and her boyfriend of seven years, Sean, are to be married in a week but both cheated on each other three days before the wedding. Faced with each of their perfect partners, Kiki and Sean ignore their responsibilities to each other and choose to go their separate ways

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Han Ming, a prosecutor, faces a whirlwind of complications in his work and family lives: his son's clash with another student in school and his wife's intervention, as well as the strained partnerships at work. Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: Crypto Storm
programme.desc: ICAC investigation officer Lok sets up a special team to investigate a corruption case involving a banks top executives use of cryptocurrency to manipulate the trading market. When the banks chairman is kidnapped and kidnappers demand ransom in crypto coins, Lok connects the dots and vows to hunt down the mastermind behind both crimes.

programme.title: 72 Tenants of Prosperity
programme.desc: Ha Kung and Shek Kin are sworn brothers, but become sworn enemies in business and every aspect of life after Pinky, the girl they love, marries Ha Kung. It is only when the property owner of both their shops wants to terminate their tenancies forty years later, that they are able to resolve the rivalry.

programme.title: Invisible Target
programme.desc: Three young police officers driven by different motives decide to join forces to defeat Tien and his lethal, mercenary gang. As they team up to prevent another massive robbery, they discover that it is instigated by another unknown man. With courage, wits and dexterity, the trio are determined to not let Tien and the instigator escape.

programme.title: Beyond the Dream
programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: Tainted Love
programme.desc: Office lady Zhou Ran falls victim to an online dating love scam and is cheated of 550,000 yuan. Following faint clues left by the scammer, Zhou Ran comes to a small coastal town and encounters two young men. She gradually discovers that these two men have hidden the clues of the scam, and sets out on her revenge plan.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Midnight Fly
programme.desc: With her marriage in crisis, Michele takes off to Europe for a vacation and meets a Japanese woman named Miki. As they become friends and travel together, Michele discovers that Miki is her husband's mistress. When Miki goes missing in Morocco, Michele does everything she can to find her but ends up paying a heavy price

programme.title: I Love Hong Kong
programme.desc: Ng Shun and his family return to the public housing estate where he grew up, not to visit his aging father, but to seek refuge after his business has failed. When his family of five squeeze into the small estate unit, Ng Shun is forced to face his long-neglected family problems...

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack

programme.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Dailys Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from a famous Japanese manga. 18-year-old Takumi delivers tofu in his father's near-obsolete car every day and becomes a good racer with perfect drifting skill. Encouraged by his father, he joins a mountain race and unexpectedly wins it, making him famous overnight and leading him from one exciting race to another.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: Moscow Mission
programme.desc: Based on the 1993 true event of the "China-Russia Train Robbery", a gang of criminals commits a heist, stealing cash and goods from the cross border train. A Chinese police officer disguises as a businessman takes charge of the operation to arrest the criminals, but uncovers a bigger conspiracy instead

programme.title: The Swift Knight
programme.desc: The Ming Emperor is dying with no heir to succeed the throne. His brother recalls that he has an illegitimate child with a court lady years ago and palace guards are sent to search for the heir. When the Emperor's nephew hires assassins to kill the child so he can be the successor, the Swift Knight comes to the rescue

programme.title: Dead End
programme.desc: Uninhibited youth Chun meets a rich girl Wen when her car breaks down and drives her home. Chun falls in love with Wen but Wens brother dislikes him and forbids his sister to see him. He humiliates Chun and gets Chun beaten up, so Chun takes the pistol he has found accidentally on the street to Wens home and shoots her brother dead.

programme.title: The Flying Dagger
programme.desc: The Yu family and the Green Dragon clan became enemies when the Yu daughter killed the clan heads son, who was a rapist and murderer. The Green Dragon leader wounds the head of the Yu family with his flying daggers, and a wandering swordsman saves the family using his own flying dagger skills. However, his allegiances and motives are unclear.

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: The Thundering Sword
programme.desc: Two disciples, Yu and Zheng, are sent by their master to track down the invincible weapon Thundering Sword to prevent villains from getting it. Yu encounters the daughter of a ruthless clan, Chiao, who is on her way to seek for the sword. They quickly fall for each other, but when Chiao accidentally injures Zheng, things become complicated.

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Muis embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love

programme.title: Enchanting Shadow
programme.desc: A young scholar Ning spends the night in a creepy temple that is said to be haunted. He does not believe in the rumours, but soon meets a beautiful female ghost Nie. Nie is forced to stay in the temple to seduce young men for a powerful demon to feast on. Knowing Nie to be a kind ghost, Ning decides to help her escape from the demons clutches.

programme.title: Hex
programme.desc: This supernatural mystery tells the story of a sickly wife and her maid conspiring to kill her beastly husband, leading to a string of events with spooky twists and turns.

programme.title: The Fighting Fool
programme.desc: Famous Kung Fu Pole master Red Eagle, is kidnapped by a villain one day. His disciple Meng, vows to rescue him. On his way, Meng encounters a greedy but great martial artist who agrees to join him in the rescue. Even though the two have extremely different personalities, they manage to team up and fight the villain in a final showdown.

programme.title: Apartment for Ladies
programme.desc: A Taiwanese singer comes to Hong Kong in search for her missing younger sister, who had arrived in Hong Kong to be discovered as a nightclub singer. She finds lodging at an apartment for women run by a man-hating landlady, Mrs Chan. However, Mrs Chan cannot confine the young ladies youthful vitality within the apartment.

programme.title: Oath Of Death
programme.desc: Three Sung loyalists become blood brothers to fight the tyranny of the Tartar invaders. To oust the oppressors altogether, Ma releases the kidnapped Tartar princess in a strategic effort to gain points with the invaders, but it soon becomes apparent that he desires both a great position and power, and will do anything to get it

programme.title: The Blue and the Black Part 2
programme.desc: Continuing from the first movie, Tang Qi ends her career as a nightclub singer and starts searching battle-scarred China for her lover Chang, who is now entangled with Japanese invaders, communist insurgents, and a warlord's beautiful daughter.

programme.title: The Mad Monk Strikes Again
programme.desc: The Mad Monk is up against the equally legendary scholar-turned-genie, Lu Tung Pin. The duo create havoc as they vie with each other, be it in mirth, magic, women or weapons!

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: A Maid From Heaven
programme.desc: The seventh daughter of the Jade Emperor is banished from heaven to live a mortal life as she is very mischievous. She falls in love with a young village lad Yong, who sold himself to work for the rich so as to bury his father. The goddess sisters help Yong to pay his debt so the lovebirds can be together. Is this going to end happily-ever-after?

programme.title: Clan Feuds
programme.desc: Like legendary director Chu Yuan did so often and so successfully, Chang Peng Yi adapted this film from a story by Ku Lung. Following the footsteps of the equally legendary Chang Cheh, Chang also casted the majestic Ti Lung, along with "Venoms Lo Meng and Sun Chien, for a spectacular showcase of mystical Martial Arts Worlds intrigue and consummate Kung Fu.

programme.title: Tiger Killer
programme.desc: Wu Song is appointed as chief constable after killing a tiger with his bare hands when drunk. The wife of his brother Wu Da Lang, seduces Wu Song but gets rejected by him, and engages in an affair with a rich man. They poison Wu Da Lang when he finds out about their affair. To avenge his brothers death, Wu Song kills both of them.

programme.title: Finger of Doom
programme.desc: The protagonists are ex-swordmasters who now find joy in making umbrellas. They track down the evil Madame Kung Sun and her poisonous Finger of Doom, a unique supernatural power which allows her to transform normal, everyday people into horrifying zombies, and this is just the start of their mythical adventure against this zombie maker!

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: What Price Honesty
programme.desc: In this period martial arts thriller, three police graduates are assigned to a town rife with crimes and corruption. They vow to uphold justice but are hampered by their corrupt superior, resulting in them putting their lives and the lives of their beloved in danger.

programme.title: Between Tears and Smiles
programme.desc: Fan Jia Shu is a kind-hearted student who is smitten with Shen, a heart-rending love song singer. However, he is not the only one who has eyes for Shen. The Generals henchmen are also determined to present the songstress to their superior as a gift. Fan receives help from an unexpected person just in time to save the woman he loves.

programme.title: The Golden Buddha
programme.desc: A map indicating the location of the Chans family heirloom is hidden in three Golden Buddha statues. Paul, an insurance agent, finds one statue by chance and Chans daughter has another one. This makes them targets of treasure-hunting criminals and they have to team up to defeat them before unveiling the hidden secrets.

programme.title: The Tigress Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Sam is being hunted as he discovers that the mayor and the chief of medical bureau are colluding with a drug dealer. He is saved by a fishermen family and works in their friends grocery but the grocery owner is killed when the enemies track Sam down. Sam escapes to Shaolin to learn the cudgel style of kung fu in order to avenge his friends.

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wongs disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption. Starring Hong Kong's premiere movie couple, it is one of the grandest Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musicals in the Shaw Brothers library.

programme.title: Rivals of Kung Fu
programme.desc: Shen and Wong Fei Hungs relationship turns sour, and Shen frames Wong and his disciple for murder. They are saved by a businessman Zhou, but Wong must win the Lion Dance Trophy to return Zhous favour. Can Wong Fei Hung defeat all skilled martial artists and complete his mission?

programme.title: The Heroic Ones
programme.desc: The story is set in the Tang Dynasty and David Chiang plays the 13th Prince, a powerful fighter whose prestigious status provokes jealously, leading to a gruesome family feud.

programme.title: Shaolin Prince
programme.desc: As the names of Chang Cheh and Liu Chia-liang became legendary, all-too-often the name of their equally valued collaborator, Tang Chia, is omitted. That may be, because, unlike the previous pair, the veteran kung-fu choreographer only went on to direct three movies of his own. Of course, that makes this trio all the more special, and this first effort perhaps the most special of all. It may be an eye-filling, mind-bending martial arts tale of two royal princes battling for the rightful recovery of the throne, but it's also a party, where Tang invites two cinematographers, three editors, and no less than five other choreographer friends to almost literally shoot the works. The results are kung-fu configurations not only never seen before, but never even imagined!

programme.title: Love without End
programme.desc: Singer Qing Qing and architect Peng Nan are a devoted couple. Qing Qing sacrifices herself to help Peng Nan when his family is going through difficulties and is misunderstood by Peng Nan, leading to their break up. When Peng Nan learns the truth and decides to make up with Qing Qing, he finds out that she is suffering from a terminal illness.

programme.title: Invincible Enforcer
programme.desc: A young man is at the wrong place at the wrong time. As he offends a police inspector, he is thrown into jail and even when released, the police goes after him until he has no choice but to become a real criminal. Only a kind and beautiful probation officer is on his side, but can she help him?

programme.title: Mr Funny - bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: The Five Venoms
programme.desc: A dying master dispatches his last pupil to track down five ex-students who are each an expert in his own lethal combat style. He fears they will steal the fortune belonging to their clan and tasks his pupil to prevent their attempt.

programme.title: Lover's Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a mans role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: Demon of the Lute
programme.desc: Lute demon Chin Mo has reappeared in the world to wreak havoc. Hsiao Feng Ling is ordered to help find a special bow and arrows that can counter the demon. Only Chiao Yin knows the whereabouts of the weapon. Hsiao and her classmate Old Naughty set out on an arduous journey to find Chiao. After overcoming many obstacles, they catch Chin Mo's man trying to snatch the bow and manage to stop him in time....

But before Israel Adesanya gears up for a title run, he has to get by surging contender Nassourdine Imavov. One of the most dominant champions of his era, Adesanya aims to get his 2025 campaign off to a winning start against Imavov, who has won three in a row leading up to the biggest fight of his career. In the co-main event, Middleweight sensation Shara Bullet Magomedov faces off with veteran star Michael Venom Page in a showdown of elite strikers.
